}); Web Domains ( domains ) This attribute is automatically populated with the domains the user has been active on. First Visit Timestamp ( firstvisit_ts ) This attribute is automatically populated with the first time the user visited the site and sends data to the default stream. Last Visit Timestamp ( lastvisit_ts ) This attribute is automatically populated with the last time the user visited the site and sends data to the default stream. Pageview Count ( pageviewct ) This attribute is automatically populated with the number of _pv events recieved for the user. JavaScript jstag.send({
  _e:"pv"
}); Referring Domain ( refdomain ) This attribute is automatically populated with the referring domain for the user. JavaScript jstag.send({
